        <h3>Therapeutic Autoethnography</h3>
        <p>My doctoral research developed a practice-based methodology built on the conviction that clinical knowledge is transmitted through story — as healers have always done for their apprentices. Published in peer-reviewed journals including the <em>European Journal of Psychotherapy &amp; Counselling</em>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

