        <h3>Gestalt Psychotherapy in Singapore</h3>
        <p>Ten years of practice across Vienna and Singapore — working with individuals, couples, and communities. My approach is experiential and relational: grounded in field theory, attentive to the body, shaped by work with asylum seekers, war trauma survivors, and the ordinary suffering of people trying to stay present to each other.</p>
